#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Email signup form for the public newsletter (double opt-in). Submits to the "
"newsletter subscribe REST endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Fomu ya kujisajili kwa barua pepe kwa jarida la barua la umma (uthibitisho "
"wa hatua mbili). Hutuma kwa endpoint ya REST ya kujisajili kwa jarida la "
"barua."

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter "
"signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer "
"template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled "
"(Settings → Newsletter)."
msgstr ""
"Kitufe cha ikoni kinachofungua dirisha ibukizi linalochukua skrini nzima "
"lenye fomu ya kujisajili kwa jarida la barua. Kinafanya kazi kivyake — "
"kiweke moja kwa moja kwenye kiolezo cha kichwa au chini ya ukurasa; "
"hakionyeshi chochote wakati jarida la umma limezimwa (Mipangilio → Jarida la "
"Barua)."

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Huorodhesha mawasilisho ya kazi za sanaa yanayosubiri ya msanii aliyeingia "
"ili yakaguliwe na kuidhinishwa. Weka hii kwenye ukurasa wako wa /my-"
"submissions/ au kwenye kiolezo cha Site Editor."

#: blocks/gallery-overview/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Proportional, randomised artwork grid across all artists. Shows featured "
"artworks first, respects per-artist budget, supports medium filtering and "
"pagination."
msgstr ""
"Mraba wa kazi za sanaa wenye uwiano na mpangilio wa nasibu kwa wasanii wote. "
"Huonyesha kwanza kazi maalum zilizoangaziwa, huheshimu bajeti ya kila msanii,"
" na inasaidia kuchuja kwa aina ya kazi na upaginishaji."

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Public application form for artists who want to join the Agnosis network. "
"Submits to the admission REST endpoint. Place this on your /join/ page."
msgstr ""
"Fomu ya maombi ya umma kwa wasanii wanaotaka kujiunga na mtandao wa Agnosis. "
"Hutumwa kwenye kiolesura cha REST cha udahili. Weka hii kwenye ukurasa wako "
"wa /join/."

#: blocks/artist-breadcrumb/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Small line identifying the artist whose subdomain is currently being viewed. "
"Renders nothing on the main Agnosis site."
msgstr ""
"Mstari mfupi unaotambulisha msanii ambaye kikoa kidogo chake kwa sasa "
"kinaonyeshwa. Huweka kitu chochote kwenye tovuti kuu ya Agnosis."

