"\n"
"Uanachama wako katika %2$s umesitishwa.\n"
"\n"
"Ikiwa una maswali, tafadhali wasiliana na msimamizi wa tovuti.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: 1: artist display name, 2: site name, 3: date
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:162
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Your membership at %2$s has been temporarily suspended until %3$s.\n"
"\n"
"You will be automatically reinstated on that date. If you have questions, "
