#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:504
msgid ""
"Images are downscaled proportionally to this width before being sent to the "
"AI for description — vision token cost scales with resolution, and a "
"description task needs far fewer pixels than the original photo. Applies to "
"artwork photo uploads, rasterised PDF pages, and video poster frames alike. "
"Set to 0 to always send full-resolution images (uses more tokens, no quality "
"difference for typical description tasks). Requires the Imagick PHP "
"extension; images are sent at their original size regardless of this setting "
"when it is unavailable. Default: 800."
msgstr ""
"Picha hupunguzwa sawia hadi upana huu kabla ya kutumwa kwa AI kwa maelezo — "
"gharama ya tokeni za kuona huongezeka kadri azimio linavyoongezeka, na kazi "
"ya maelezo inahitaji pikseli chache zaidi kuliko picha asili. Hutumika kwa "
"upakiaji wa picha za kazi ya sanaa, kurasa za PDF zilizogeuzwa rasteri, na "
"fremu za bango la video kwa pamoja. Weka 0 ili kila mara utume picha kwa "
"azimio kamili (hutumia tokeni zaidi, hakuna tofauti ya ubora kwa kazi za "
"maelezo za kawaida). Inahitaji kiendelezi cha PHP cha Imagick; picha hutumwa "
"kwa ukubwa wake wa asili bila kujali mpangilio huu inapokosekana. Chaguo "
"msingi: 800."

