msgid ""
"The application by %s has closed without reaching the admission threshold. "
"No action required."
msgstr ""
"Ombi la %s limefungwa bila kufikia kiwango cha kuingizwa. Hakuna hatua "
"inayohitajika."

#: includes/AI/PromptConfig.php:86
msgid ""
"The artist sent no subject line or message with this submission — let the "
"image speak entirely for itself."
msgstr ""
"Msanii hakutuma kichwa cha mada wala ujumbe pamoja na uwasilishaji huu — "
"acha picha izungumze kabisa yenyewe."

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:133
msgid "The artwork has been published to the gallery."
msgstr "Kazi ya sanaa imechapishwa kwenye ghala."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:821
msgid ""
"The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight "
"on, with the camera parallel to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Kazi ya sanaa imepigwa picha kwa pembe, ikisababisha upotoshaji. Piga moja "
"kwa moja, na kamera ikiwa sambamba na turubai."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:375
msgid ""
"The artwork itself has not been altered — only the photograph quality was "
"corrected."
msgstr ""
"Kazi ya sanaa yenyewe haijabadilishwa — ubora wa picha pekee ndio "
"uliorekebishwa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:822
msgid ""
"The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in "
"front of the artwork, parallel to its surface."
msgstr ""
"Kazi ya sanaa inaonekana kupotoshwa au kupinda. Weka kamera yako moja kwa "
"moja mbele ya kazi ya sanaa, sambamba na uso wake."

#: includes/Artist/CommunityCapVote.php:96
msgid "The cap must be zero or a positive number."
msgstr "Kikomo lazima kiwe sifuri au nambari chanya."

#. translators: %d: number of days
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:342
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The community has %d days to vote. We will let you know the outcome by email."
msgstr ""
"Jamii ina siku %d za kupiga kura. Tutakujulisha matokeo kwa barua pepe."

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:368
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The community removal vote has closed with a majority in favour.\n"
"\n"
"The artist's account and all published work have been permanently deleted "
"from %1$s.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Kura ya kuondoa mwanajumuiya imefungwa kwa wingi wa kura za kuunga mkono.\n"
"\n"
"Akaunti ya msanii na kazi zote zilizochapishwa zimefutwa kabisa kutoka %1$s."
"\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:394
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The community removal vote has closed. The required majority was not reached "
"and the artist's membership remains active.\n"
"\n"
"— %s"
msgstr ""
"Kura ya kuondoa mwanajumuiya imefungwa. Wingi unaohitajika wa kura "
"haukufikiwa na uanachama wa msanii unabaki hai.\n"
"\n"
"— %s"

#. translators: 1: proposed cap, 2: proposal id
#: includes/Artist/CommunityCapNotification.php:107
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The community voted to change the membership size cap to %1$s (proposal "
"#%2$d). The new cap is now in effect."
msgstr ""
"Jumuiya ilipiga kura ya kubadili kiwango cha juu cha ukubwa wa uanachama "
"hadi %1$s (pendekezo #%2$d). Kikomo kipya sasa kinatumika."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:806
msgid ""
"The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the "
"self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus "
"locks on it."
msgstr ""
"Picha imekuwa butu. Weka simu au kamera yako juu ya uso thabiti, tumia "
"kipima muda, na hakikisha kazi ya sanaa inachukua sehemu kubwa ya fremu ili "
"autofocus ifunge juu yake."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:807
msgid ""
"The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before "
"shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still."
msgstr ""
"Picha haina umakini. Gusa kazi ya sanaa kwenye skrini ya simu yako kabla ya "
"kupiga ili kuhakikisha autofocus inafunga juu yake, na shikilia kamera bila "
"kuyumba."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:813
msgid ""
"The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting "
"on your camera."
msgstr ""
"Picha ina pikseli zinazoonekana. Piga kutoka karibu zaidi au tumia mpangilio "
"wa azimio la juu zaidi kwenye kamera yako."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:812
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and fill the frame with the artwork."
msgstr ""
"Azimio la picha ni la chini sana. Tumia mpangilio wa ubora wa juu zaidi wa "
"simu yako na ijaze fremu kwa kazi ya sanaa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:811
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and make sure you're close enough that the artwork fills the frame."
msgstr ""
"Azimio la picha ni la chini sana. Tumia mpangilio wa ubora wa juu zaidi wa "
"simu yako na hakikisha uko karibu vya kutosha ili kazi ya sanaa ijaze fremu."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:912
msgid ""
"The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork "
"clearly."
msgstr ""
"Ubora wa jumla wa picha ulikuwa chini sana kwa AI yetu kuweza kuchakata kazi "
"ya sanaa kwa uwazi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:818
msgid ""
"The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural "
"light source or adjust your camera's white balance."
msgstr ""
"Picha ina madoido ya buluu baridi. Hamisha kazi ya sanaa kwenye chanzo cha "
"mwanga chenye joto zaidi na cha asili zaidi au rekebisha white balance ya "
"kamera yako."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:815
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:816
msgid ""
"The photo has a strong colour cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your "
"phone's Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colours."
msgstr ""
"Picha ina mkengeuko mkali wa rangi. Piga chini ya mwanga wa asili usio na "
"rangi au tumia mpangilio wa Auto White Balance wa simu yako kwa rangi sahihi "
"zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:801
msgid ""
"The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or "
"flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best."
msgstr ""
"Picha imefichuliwa kupita kiasi (nuru sana / imeoshwa). Epuka mwanga wa jua "
"wa moja kwa moja au flash iliyolenga moja kwa moja kwenye kazi ya sanaa — "
"mwanga uliosambaa au wa upande wa pili hufanya kazi vizuri zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:802
msgid ""
"The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — "
"diffuse light or shade gives more even tones."
msgstr ""
"Picha ni ya kung'aa sana au imeoshwa. Epuka mwanga wa jua wa moja kwa moja "
"au flash — mwanga uliosambaa au kivuli hutoa toni zilizo sawa zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:799
msgid ""
"The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a "
"large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side."
msgstr ""
"Picha ni nyeusi sana kuonyesha kazi yako ya sanaa waziwazi. Jaribu kupiga "
"picha karibu na dirisha kubwa wakati wa mchana, au tumia taa laini "
"iliyoelekezwa kwenye kazi kutoka upande."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:800
msgid ""
"The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window "
"in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side."
msgstr ""
"Picha haijafichuliwa vizuri (ni nyeusi sana). Jaribu kupiga picha karibu na "
"dirisha kubwa wakati wa mchana, au tumia taa laini iliyoelekezwa kwenye kazi "
"kutoka upande."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:817
msgid ""
"The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch "
"your phone's white balance to Daylight / Cloudy."
msgstr ""
"Picha inaonekana ya njano sana au ya joto. Piga chini ya mwanga wa asili wa "
"mchana au badilisha white balance ya simu yako kuwa Daylight / Cloudy."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:513
msgid ""
"The Publish and Discard links above expire in 7 days. Your submission stays "
"as a draft until you decide."
msgstr ""
"Viungo vya Chapisha na Tupa vilivyo hapo juu vitaisha baada ya siku 7. "
"Uwasilishaji wako unabaki kama rasimu hadi uamue."

#: includes/Publishing/RemovalEndpoints.php:204
msgid "The removal link has expired. Please send another removal request."
msgstr ""
"Kiungo cha uondoaji muda wake umeisha. Tafadhali tuma ombi jingine la "
"uondoaji."

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:134
msgid "The submission has been discarded."
msgstr "Uwasilishaji umetupiliwa mbali."

#: includes/Artist/ContentEditor.php:231
msgid "The title cannot be empty."
msgstr "Kichwa hakiwezi kuwa tupu."

#: includes/Artist/ContentEditor.php:328
msgid "The uploaded file could not be read."
msgstr "Faili iliyopakiwa haikuweza kusomwa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:804
msgid ""
"There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or "
"change your angle to eliminate it."
msgstr ""
"Kuna mwangwi juu ya uso wa kazi ya sanaa. Inamisha turubai kidogo au "
"badilisha pembe yako ili kuuondoa."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:823
msgid ""
"There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source "
"or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface."
msgstr ""
"Kuna kivuli juu ya sehemu ya kazi ya sanaa. Hamisha chanzo chako cha mwanga "
"au songesha kazi ya sanaa ili hakuna vivuli vitakavyoanguka juu ya uso."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:803
msgid ""
"There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas "
"slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface."
msgstr ""
"Kuna mng'ao au mwangwi mkali juu ya kazi ya sanaa. Inamisha turubai kidogo "
"au piga picha kwa pembe ili kuondoa mwangwi kutoka kwenye uso."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:808
msgid ""
"There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the "
"shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake."
msgstr ""
"Kuna ukungu wa mwendo. Shikilia kamera bila kuyumba sana au tumia tripod; "
"bonyeza kitufe cha kupiga kwa upole au tumia kipima muda ili kuepuka "
"mtikisiko."

#: includes/Artist/ContentEditor.php:407
msgid "There is no photo to restore."
msgstr "Hakuna picha ya kurejesha."

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:238
msgid ""
"This community is currently full. Your application has joined the waitlist — "
"when a member leaves, the next person in line is welcomed in, and the "
"community can also vote to make room for more artists."
msgstr ""
"Jamii hii kwa sasa imejaa. Ombi lako limeongezwa kwenye orodha ya kusubiri — "
"mwanajamii akiondoka, mtu anayefuata kwenye foleni hupokelewa, na jamii pia "
"inaweza kupiga kura ili kutengeneza nafasi kwa wasanii zaidi."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:283
msgid "This confirmation link expires in 7 days."
msgstr "Kiungo hiki cha uthibitisho kitaisha baada ya siku 7."

